297
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:19,940
I enjoy this too.

298
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:22,540
It felt lonely
when it was just my son and me

299
00:13:22,540 --> 00:13:23,355
in the dormitory.

300
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,140
It's good now.

301
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:26,380
It really feels like home.

302
00:13:28,288 --> 00:13:29,088
Let me do it.

303
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:30,500
Come and see.

304
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:33,180
Mr. Shen prepared this for you.

305
00:13:33,466 --> 00:13:34,180
It's pure cotton.

306
00:13:34,420 --> 00:13:35,580
He has sensitive skin

307
00:13:35,666 --> 00:13:37,260
and likes things made of pure cotton.

308
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:38,780
It's pure cotton. Feel it.

309
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:40,740
Thank you.

310
00:13:42,377 --> 00:13:43,620
