311
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:44,980
Didn't I tell you?

312
00:13:45,780 --> 00:13:46,500
We're a family.

313
00:13:47,577 --> 00:13:48,688
No need to thank me.

314
00:13:48,940 --> 00:13:49,340
Okay.

315
00:13:51,933 --> 00:13:53,420
Alright, you should rest early.

316
00:13:53,866 --> 00:13:54,755
Speaking of,

317
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:56,180
if you need

318
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:57,580
or want anything,

319
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:58,540
just tell me.

320
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,220
You can also tell your mom.

321
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:02,700
Okay.

322
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:04,460
Get some rest.

323
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:05,100
Okay.

324
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:06,940
Look, it's warm and cozy.

325
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,000
Go to bed early.

326
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:09,820
Okay, Mom.

327
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,909
