330
00:14:18,420 --> 00:14:19,100
It's fine.

331
00:14:19,244 --> 00:14:21,133
He's a child.
Having a door is good enough.

332
00:14:21,180 --> 00:14:21,822
Don't bother.

333
00:14:23,088 --> 00:14:24,844
I have to fix the things one by one.

334
00:14:24,888 --> 00:14:25,422
Take a break.

335
00:14:25,444 --> 00:14:26,510
I'll fix the door tomorrow.

336
00:14:27,940 --> 00:14:29,044
There are so many things.

337
00:14:29,288 --> 00:14:30,460
Here. Let's tidy up together.

338
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,140
No, hurry up.

339
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:33,540
Hurry and sit down.

340
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:34,740
No need to help me out.

341
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:35,500
Alright?

342
00:14:35,860 --> 00:14:36,140
Fine.

343
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:38,060
I'll just rest my old back.

344
00:14:38,422 --> 00:14:39,720
You've been busy for half a day.

345
00:14:47,180 --> 00:14:48,980
Did Lian Jin paint these?

346
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:50,140
Yes.

347
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:52,460
He likes to paint.

348
00:14:56,780 --> 00:14:57,900
This is very special.

349
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,380
These paintings are interesting.

350
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:05,700
I can take Lian Jin's paintings

351
00:15:06,140 --> 00:15:07,780
to my old friends
at the publishing house

352
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:08,940
to show them one day.

353
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,380
I'll ask them

354
00:15:10,860 --> 00:15:12,700
to give Lian Jin some illustration jobs.

355
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:13,540
Isn't that great?

356
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:15,300
Can Lian Jin

357
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:18,180
draw illustrations?

358
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:19,900
Why not? Look how interesting

359
00:15:20,044 --> 00:15:21,020
these paintings are.

360
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:24,260
Editors like artists with personality.

361
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:25,540
Is that so?

362
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:28,980
I didn't expect it.

363
00:15:29,660 --> 00:15:30,300
It's really...

364
00:15:30,866 --> 00:15:32,980
Lian Jin will definitely be happy
if he finds out.

365
00:15:33,622 --> 00:15:34,540
Did he also paint that?

366
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:35,940
Yes. He painted this

367
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,740
when he was in Year 4.

368
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:39,940
He painted himself.

369
00:15:40,820 --> 00:15:41,580
A self-portrait?

370
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,260
Yes.

371
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:45,540
He loves to draw paintings like this.

372
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:48,540
Interesting.

373
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:51,780
I

374
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:53,300
read a book

375
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:55,980
about the psychology of painting.

376
00:15:58,020 --> 00:15:59,060
It says

377
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:02,020
that painters blur the eyes consciously.

378
00:16:04,700 --> 00:16:05,900
It's a way for the painter

379
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:07,820
to cover up.

380
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:10,580
They hide themselves,

381
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:12,380
unwilling to reveal their true self.

382
00:16:13,355 --> 00:16:15,660
I have to admit
that what you said is pretty accurate.

383
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:18,380
Lian Jin is introverted.

384
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:19,980
He doesn't tell me anything.

385
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:21,660
I don't know what he's thinking.

386
00:16:22,340 --> 00:16:23,380
Unlike Dai,

387
00:16:24,020 --> 00:16:25,580
who says whatever she wants.

388
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:27,940
After arguing with everyone,

389
00:16:27,940 --> 00:16:29,600
she still gets along with them.
How nice.

390
00:16:30,660 --> 00:16:31,540
In this vast world,

391
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:33,140
how can everyone be the same?

392
00:16:35,177 --> 00:16:37,180
All that matters is the children
are well-behaved.

393
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:37,820
Yes.

394
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:39,980
I like this painting.

395
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,500
We should hang it up.

396
00:16:44,955 --> 00:16:45,711
Speaking of,

397
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:47,420
there's another important thing.

398
00:16:48,020 --> 00:16:49,220
Let's find time

399
00:16:49,700 --> 00:16:51,460
to have a meal together.

400
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:54,420
Invite all the children.

401
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:55,500
We'll

402
00:16:55,888 --> 00:16:57,060
formally introduce Lian Jin.

403
00:17:01,900 --> 00:17:02,380
Great.

404
00:17:03,180 --> 00:17:03,940
Thank you.

405
00:17:07,740 --> 00:17:09,060
Shen Qing, bring Lina and Duole

406
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:10,260
to my place next weekend

407
00:17:10,540 --> 00:17:11,900
for a family meeting.

408
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:13,933
I have something to discuss with you.

409
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:17,100
What can it be?

410
00:17:17,860 --> 00:17:19,660
Is it about Ms. Lian's son?

411
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:26,420
What should we do?

412
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:29,220
This is a formal meeting.

413
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,020
Should we give him a red envelope?

414
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:34,500
What red envelope?

415
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:35,955
We're of the same status.

416
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:37,460
Yes.

417
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,955
He's considered your younger brother.

418
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:44,260
Discuss?

419
00:17:45,220 --> 00:17:46,740
It's a done deal.

420
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:48,020
What's there to discuss?

421
00:17:48,380 --> 00:17:48,740
Duole.

422
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:51,177
Don't join the meeting.

423
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:52,940
I'm joining.

424
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,620
I want to meet Lian Jin.

425
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:56,860
Dad asked Duole to go.

426
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:59,540
Besides, he should join out of courtesy.

427
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:01,740
Shen Duole.

428
00:18:02,260 --> 00:18:04,260
He's considered your uncle.

429
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:05,800
Don't talk too much when you go.

430
00:18:07,177 --> 00:18:08,866
I don't have to call him Uncle, right?

431
00:18:09,155 --> 00:18:10,660
He's only a few years older than me.

432
00:18:10,866 --> 00:18:11,580
Alright, Duole.

433
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:12,420
Go to bed.

434
00:18:23,866 --> 00:18:25,000
Are you not going to bed?

435
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:27,500
I'm not sleepy at all.

436
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:34,900
What did you say?

437
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:37,340
Her son moved in?

438
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,340
You're doomed.

439
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,900
What did I say?

440
00:18:43,711 --> 00:18:45,333
Ms. Lian has favorable qualities.

441
00:18:45,466 --> 00:18:46,740
What did she see in that old man?

442
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:49,260
The truth is out now, right?

443
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:51,660
She's about to show her true intentions.

444
00:18:52,111 --> 00:18:53,060
Keep your voice down.

445
00:18:53,300 --> 00:18:54,580
Shen Qing is still asleep.

446
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:56,660
Their company recently

447
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:58,020
bought a foreign patent

448
00:18:58,900 --> 00:19:01,260
and is holding international meetings
every day.

449
00:19:01,288 --> 00:19:02,644
Their day and night are reversed.

450
00:19:03,820 --> 00:19:04,500
He works hard.

451
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,740
He works so hard.

452
00:19:06,180 --> 00:19:08,060
By the way, you should tell Shen Qing

453
00:19:08,260 --> 00:19:09,580
not to work so hard.

454
00:19:10,140 --> 00:19:11,780
I've said it many times. It's useless.

455
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:13,260
I'm making soup for him.

456
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:15,140
Ms. Lian's health-preserving recipe.

457
00:19:17,900 --> 00:19:18,700
Ms. Lian

458
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:21,380
reached out
to everyone in the Shen family.

459
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:23,820
She first
got close to you and Shen Qing.

460
00:19:24,780 --> 00:19:25,220
Later,

461
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:27,580
she conquered Shen Dai.

462
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:30,180
In the end, the mother and son

463
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:33,460
have a triumphant reunion
in the Shen family's place.

464
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:35,340
Listen to yourself.

465
00:19:35,755 --> 00:19:37,300
You make it sound like a spy movie.

466
00:19:39,460 --> 00:19:41,340
Are they getting married?

467
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:44,980
Or does she want the old man
to raise her son?

468
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,020
Or is she

469
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:49,220
after the free housing?

470
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:50,780
How would I know?

471
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:51,980
You must know.

472
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,660
You all need to be on...

473
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:54,980
On high alert.

474
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:57,100
Protect the family property. Got it?

475
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:58,540
Well...

476
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:00,940
Mom, you came.

477
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:01,780
You woke up.

478
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:04,060
Na just mentioned you.

479
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:05,890
She said
you've been working very hard lately,

480
00:20:05,890 --> 00:20:06,911
so she made soup for you.

481
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:07,940
Drink it later.

482
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:10,660
I bought some baby spinach today.

483
00:20:10,711 --> 00:20:12,866
They're very fresh.
I'll stir-fry a plate for you later

484
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:13,666
to boost your iron.

485
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:14,540
Mom.

486
00:20:15,060 --> 00:20:18,100
Well, it's convenient for us
to buy vegetables.

487
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:18,780
Thank you.

488
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:20,511
No need
to buy vegetables for us anymore.

489
00:20:21,422 --> 00:20:22,580
My vegetables are different.

490
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:23,860
I buy vegetables from farmers.

491
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:24,860
They're organic.

492
00:20:26,111 --> 00:20:26,711
Speaking of...

493
00:20:27,580 --> 00:20:27,980
Well...

494
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:29,300
Shen Qing.

495
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:32,020
I want to ask you.

496
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:33,860
Ms. Lian's son

497
00:20:36,220 --> 00:20:38,220
has moved in, right?

498
00:20:39,940 --> 00:20:41,060
Is your father going

499
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:43,020
to marry Ms. Lian?

500
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:45,533
I don't know either.

501
00:20:46,340 --> 00:20:47,020
I respect

502
00:20:47,444 --> 00:20:49,000
