- Help someone else raise their son.

511
00:21:08,622 --> 00:21:09,244
- I...
- Try it.

512
00:21:09,266 --> 00:21:10,755
- I don't want to drink it.
- Try it.

513
00:21:11,044 --> 00:21:11,680
It smells good.

514
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:12,644
It smells good, right?

515
00:21:12,688 --> 00:21:15,422
Isn't the painting Lian Jin painted
when he was a child interesting?

516
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:17,060
Look at the lines

517
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:18,100
and colors.

518
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:19,860
How creative.

519
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,260
It's really good.

520
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:22,860
Right?

521
00:21:22,860 --> 00:21:24,380
Let me take a photo to study.

522
00:21:26,222 --> 00:21:27,600
- Here.
- You're even taking a photo?

523
00:21:27,622 --> 00:21:28,955
You two, get to know each other.

524
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:31,140
You must be Lian Jin.

525
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:34,180
I'm Shen Duole.

526
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:36,466
That's a nice painting. You painted it?

527
00:21:38,140 --> 00:21:38,980
You two

528
00:21:39,088 --> 00:21:40,260
are only five years apart.

529
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:42,020
From now on,

530
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,740
call each other by your first names.

531
00:21:43,977 --> 00:21:45,220
It makes communication easier.

532
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:45,500
Okay.

533
00:21:46,220 --> 00:21:47,111
Duole, come here.

534
00:21:47,155 --> 00:21:48,688
Be good. Come over and sit down.

535
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:50,100
Lian Jin, let me tell you.

536
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:51,660
Duole is good at basketball.

537
00:21:51,700 --> 00:21:53,300
You can go play basketball with him.

538
00:21:58,460 --> 00:21:59,220
Ms. Lian, sit down.

539
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:00,300
- Yes.
- Ms. Lian.

540
00:22:00,300 --> 00:22:00,700
No need.

541
00:22:00,700 --> 00:22:02,090
No need to squeeze with each other.

542
00:22:02,090 --> 00:22:03,020
I'll just sit here.

543
00:22:03,488 --> 00:22:04,540
- Sure.
- I'll sit here.

544
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:06,100
Okay, everyone is seated.

545
00:22:06,533 --> 00:22:08,355
