- Hello.

552
00:22:20,177 --> 00:22:20,622
Hello.

553
00:22:21,155 --> 00:22:22,133
-Hello.
- Hello.

554
00:22:23,500 --> 00:22:24,300
I'm sorry.

555
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:26,020
He's a bit introverted.

556
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:29,700
Lian Jin has officially moved in.

557
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:31,340
I feel good.

558
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:33,980
We're now

559
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:35,500
a big happy family.

560
00:22:37,100 --> 00:22:38,820
By the way, he's staying in the study.

561
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:40,380
I've cleared out the study.

562
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:42,740
The study faces south

563
00:22:42,977 --> 00:22:44,180
and has plenty of sunlight.

564
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:46,620
It will help him recover.

565
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:53,420
Lian Jin is bookish.

566
00:22:54,300 --> 00:22:55,180
He's a literary youth.

567
00:22:56,900 --> 00:22:57,300
Grandpa.

568
00:22:57,860 --> 00:22:59,660
You found someone to recite poetry
this time.

569
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,300
That's right.

570
00:23:00,660 --> 00:23:01,100
Lian Jin.

571
00:23:01,311 --> 00:23:02,410
Do you play Honor of Kings?

572
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:03,377
