577
00:23:13,688 --> 00:23:15,300
By the way, Lina,
there's one more thing.

578
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:18,100
Ms. Lian has to go to work
during the day.

579
00:23:18,820 --> 00:23:19,860
Lian Jin...

