00:23:19,977 --> 00:23:20,660
I'll handle it.

581
00:23:20,955 --> 00:23:22,500
It's just adding a pair of chopsticks.

582
00:23:22,620 --> 00:23:23,260
Yes.

583
00:23:24,220 --> 00:23:24,860
Thank you.

584
00:23:25,300 --> 00:23:26,300
That's what I mean.

585
00:23:27,288 --> 00:23:28,860
Alright, you can rest assured now.

586
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:30,740
This is why we bought our houses

587
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:31,540
opposite each other.

588
00:23:31,540 --> 00:23:33,288
It's convenient
to take care of each other.

589
00:23:34,060 --> 00:23:35,340
Sorry to bother you.

590
00:23:36,140 --> 00:23:36,740
No.

591
00:23:38,060 --> 00:23:38,580
Look at you.

592
00:23:39,300 --> 00:23:41,420
Why keep saying things like this
when we're family?

593
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:42,780
How is it a bother?

594
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,780
Don't say it anymore.

595
00:23:47,577 --> 00:23:48,711
Speaking of,

596
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:50,900
move the desk

597
00:23:51,180 --> 00:23:52,780
from that room

598
00:23:52,780 --> 00:23:54,140
to the living room.

599
00:23:54,533 --> 00:23:56,422
I'll be writing and reading here
from now on.

600
00:23:56,644 --> 00:23:57,377
Besides,

601
00:23:57,540 --> 00:23:59,100
I bought a bed too.

602
00:23:59,577 --> 00:24:00,755
I installed it afterward.

603
00:24:00,777 --> 00:24:01,844
Somehow it keeps shaking.

604
00:24:01,844 --> 00:24:02,466
Check it out.

605
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:04,620
Also,

606
00:24:05,220 --> 00:24:07,620
tell Dai about this.

607
00:24:11,020 --> 00:24:12,020
Grandpa, let me move it.

608
00:24:12,780 --> 00:24:13,540
You're really smug.

609
00:24:13,540 --> 00:24:14,420
Sit down.

610
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:15,311
Open your shoulders.

611
00:24:15,660 --> 00:24:16,820
I'll go. I'll move it.

612
00:24:21,580 --> 00:24:23,260
By the way, move the books first.

613
00:24:24,100 --> 00:24:24,580
Alright.

614
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:27,900
I'll go help.

615
00:24:31,222 --> 00:24:32,822
You can talk about Honor of Kings now.

616
00:24:32,822 --> 00:24:33,660
He doesn't play it.

617
00:24:34,060 --> 00:24:34,380
Really?

618
00:24:35,220 --> 00:24:35,780
So good.

619
00:24:38,380 --> 00:24:38,700
Dad.

620
00:24:39,422 --> 00:24:40,333
I took everything out.

621
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:43,140
You moved everything, right?

622
00:24:43,140 --> 00:24:43,820
Okay.

623
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:46,600
Look at you, you're so inactive
that you're tired and gasping for breath.

624
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:47,866
You just did a little bit of work.

625
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:49,044
You're even worse than me.

626
00:24:50,155 --> 00:24:51,460
Have you stopped running recently?

627
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:53,820
I haven't had time to run recently.

628
00:24:55,860 --> 00:24:57,140
Practice Tai Chi then.

629
00:24:57,444 --> 00:24:58,577
It's dynamic and static.

630
00:24:59,044 --> 00:25:00,080
It's good for your health.

631
00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:03,180
Dad.

632
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:06,100
Your main job now
is health preservation.

633
00:25:06,420 --> 00:25:08,060
How can Shen Qing compare with you?

634
00:25:08,180 --> 00:25:10,260
He's busy in the office all day.

635
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:11,300
Standing up and walking

636
00:25:11,300 --> 00:25:12,400
can be considered exercise.

637
00:25:12,940 --> 00:25:14,620
Only you can order him around.

638
00:25:14,777 --> 00:25:16,400
Mr. Shen
is a level-one protected species

639
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,340
in our home.

640
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:19,380
I do all the heavy work.

641
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:20,740
Okay, stop talking.

642
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:23,380
Alright, stop talking.

643
00:25:23,420 --> 00:25:24,100
Here. Go home.

644
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:24,940
I...

645
00:25:25,133 --> 00:25:25,780
Alright, go home.

646
00:25:25,822 --> 00:25:26,311
I'll do it.

647
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:27,580
Go home. Go back and rest.

648
00:25:27,700 --> 00:25:28,020
Okay.

649
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:32,100
Go.

650
00:25:32,177 --> 00:25:33,140
Ms. Lian, we're leaving.

651
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:35,260
I wanted to serve you some water.

652
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:35,940
It's fine.

653
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:40,180
Bye, Dad.

654
00:25:45,177 --> 00:25:46,540
We were kicked out just like that?

655
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:48,300
Do you want to complain about it?

656
00:26:00,780 --> 00:26:01,700
Silence at last.

657
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:04,220
You worked hard.

658
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:06,780
You worked hard.

659
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:10,540
Thank you. My son and I
have someone to rely on now.

660
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:11,660
Look.

661
00:26:11,866 --> 00:26:13,488
Why are you saying thank you again?

662
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:17,220
Thank you.

663
00:26:18,340 --> 00:26:19,540
No, don't say it. Look.

664
00:26:19,666 --> 00:26:21,222
If you say it, he will say it too.

665
00:26:21,260 --> 00:26:21,900
Didn't I say it?

666
00:26:21,940 --> 00:26:23,450
We're a family. No need to be formal.

667
00:26:23,820 --> 00:26:24,577
We're a family.

668
00:26:28,180 --> 00:26:30,420
Lian Jin, I'll get two books

669
00:26:30,460 --> 00:26:31,220
from your room,

670
00:26:31,420 --> 00:26:32,820
and you can go back to rest. Okay?

671
00:26:33,780 --> 00:26:34,100
Sure.

672
00:26:56,733 --> 00:26:58,500
Can you
please stop fiddling with the door?

673
00:26:58,500 --> 00:26:59,980
No, what's wrong with this door?

674
00:26:59,980 --> 00:27:01,660
The rail on top of this door

675
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:02,740
is quite smooth.

676
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:04,460
Why can't it be closed tightly?

677
00:27:05,180 --> 00:27:05,660
It's fine.

678
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:06,800
It can't be closed tightly.

679
00:27:06,844 --> 00:27:07,940
Lian Jin can't sleep well.

680
00:27:08,220 --> 00:27:09,020
He's a child.

681
00:27:09,780 --> 00:27:11,820
He can sleep like a log. It's okay.

682
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:13,140
No.

683
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:13,940
We need

684
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:16,300
to find a carpenter to fix this.

685
00:27:16,300 --> 00:27:17,380
I can't fix it.

686
00:27:18,860 --> 00:27:20,500
Go rest. You've had a busy night.

687
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:25,340
Lian Jin.

688
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:27,540
Rest early.

689
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:29,180
Okay, Mom.

690
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:37,740
Okay.

691
00:27:42,980 --> 00:27:43,380
Look.

692
00:27:43,980 --> 00:27:44,380
I

693
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:46,020
prepared everything for you.

694
00:27:46,577 --> 00:27:47,444
Look at me.

695
00:27:47,444 --> 00:27:48,266
Check the temperature.

696
00:27:48,288 --> 00:27:49,488
You even brought the water over.

697
00:27:49,511 --> 00:27:50,222
Here, let me do it.

698
00:27:50,911 --> 00:27:51,460
Look at this.

699
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:52,220
Here.

700
00:27:54,020 --> 00:27:54,540
Here.

701
00:27:56,980 --> 00:27:58,266
You exhausted yourself today.

702
00:27:58,580 --> 00:27:59,180
No.

703
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:00,500
Almost there.

704
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:02,780
Is it hot?

705
00:28:02,955 --> 00:28:04,066
- Is it okay?
- It's good.

706
00:28:06,740 --> 00:28:08,740
Soak your feet more often
when you're free.

707
00:28:10,860 --> 00:28:12,940
Isn't this only possible
because of your presence?

708
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:16,940
Be serious.

709
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:44,100
Dear, drink some water.

710
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:48,940
It's alright

711
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:50,780
that the child is in poor health,

712
00:28:51,180 --> 00:28:52,980
but he has a weird temper.

713
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:55,460
Why didn't Ms. Lian

714
00:28:55,780 --> 00:28:57,660
tell us?

715
00:28:58,300 --> 00:29:00,460
She must know that we won't agree to it.

716
00:29:01,620 --> 00:29:03,420
Why does she need to tell you?

717
00:29:03,860 --> 00:29:05,100
She just needs to tell Dad.

718
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:06,660
Why didn't Dad tell me then?

719
00:29:07,060 --> 00:29:08,060
How would I know?

720
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:10,500
Your dad tells everyone everything.

721
00:29:11,420 --> 00:29:13,860
This matter
is closely related to you and me.

722
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:15,980
You now have a new brother.

723
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:20,820
Shen Qing.

724
00:29:21,088 --> 00:29:23,060
If I bring back
a child I had with someone else,

725
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:24,420
will you accept them?

726
00:29:25,020 --> 00:29:25,860
Yes.

727
00:29:25,933 --> 00:29:27,740
They're the future of the country
after all.

728
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,620
What's that supposed to mean?

729
00:29:29,644 --> 00:29:31,020
Do you already have one outside?

730
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:31,980
I'm telling you.

731
00:29:32,300 --> 00:29:34,500
I won't tolerate any nonsense.

732
00:29:34,577 --> 00:29:36,180
I'm telling you. Let me know in advance

733
00:29:36,180 --> 00:29:37,620
if you have one.

734
00:29:37,711 --> 00:29:39,820
I'll get divorced
and make room for you right away.

735
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:42,700
What is that?

736
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:44,239
What time are you going to bed?

737
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:46,133
- I'm not sleeping.
- You can never finish work.

738
00:29:47,020 --> 00:29:47,580
Jeez.

739
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:49,540
Lian Jin.

740
00:29:51,300 --> 00:29:51,740
Lian Jin.

741
00:29:56,688 --> 00:29:57,620
What's wrong, Mom?

742
00:29:57,688 --> 00:29:58,466
You're not asleep?

743
00:29:59,180 --> 00:29:59,900
Not yet.

744
00:30:00,266 --> 00:30:02,688
I know you're not asleep
when I see you've got the light on.

745
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:06,180
Were you reading again?

746
00:30:07,133 --> 00:30:09,777
Get up early and go to bed early.
Don't stay up late all the time.

747
00:30:09,780 --> 00:30:11,060
Your body can't take it.

748
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:11,900
Okay.

749
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:15,180
Mom.

750
00:30:17,066 --> 00:30:19,460
I'm not used to
new bed.

751
00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:23,060
You'll adapt to it after some time.

752
00:30:25,020 --> 00:30:25,740
The house keys.

753
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,733
Keep it well.

754
00:30:31,288 --> 00:30:33,355
Do I have to put them
around my neck like this?

755
00:30:34,140 --> 00:30:34,460
Mom.

756
00:30:35,288 --> 00:30:36,822
Do you think I'm a three-year-old kid?

757
00:30:38,822 --> 00:30:39,888
What's the matter?

758
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:41,888
Even if you're 80 years old,
you're still my son.

759
00:30:41,933 --> 00:30:42,888
You want to rebel?

760
00:30:44,060 --> 00:30:44,620
No.

761
00:30:45,500 --> 00:30:47,060
But you remind me

762
00:30:47,060 --> 00:30:48,020
of when you were a kid.

763
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:51,000
You wore a bunch of keys
around your neck.

764
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,780
You have a big head

765
00:30:51,860 --> 00:30:53,100
and a thin neck.

766
00:30:53,220 --> 00:30:54,860
They jingled.

767
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:57,340
I knew from afar that my son was home.

768
00:30:57,860 --> 00:30:59,140
And I felt at ease.

769
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:04,460
I

770
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:06,100
jingled the keys

771
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:08,100
so that you knew I was home.

772
00:31:09,260 --> 00:31:09,700
Really?

773
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,860
You're quite thoughtful.

774
00:31:13,020 --> 00:31:13,820
Hurry. Go to bed.

775
00:31:16,740 --> 00:31:18,500
You need to rest.

776
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:19,900
It's my fault

777
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:21,410
for not taking good care of you

778
00:31:22,100 --> 00:31:22,820
and troubling you.

779
00:31:24,460 --> 00:31:26,340
I was busy
with work and hometown matters.

780
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:28,740
I didn't bother
with my most beloved child.

781
00:31:29,700 --> 00:31:30,020
Mom.

782
00:31:30,780 --> 00:31:31,500
Don't say that.

783
00:31:35,622 --> 00:31:36,780
Take good care of yourself.

784
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:38,180
When you recover,

785
00:31:39,340 --> 00:31:40,220
we'll go traveling.

786
00:31:41,266 --> 00:31:42,355
Where do you want to go?

787
00:31:43,177 --> 00:31:45,060
By the way,
you mentioned Sanya last time.

788
00:31:45,220 --> 00:31:46,340
Why don't we go to Sanya?

789
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:48,620
Sure.

790
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:52,660
Can we not bring that old man?

791
00:31:54,911 --> 00:31:55,955
That old man?

792
00:31:58,500 --> 00:31:59,620
Is he that old?

793
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:05,700
Will you two get married?

794
00:32:11,222 --> 00:32:12,220
What do you want to say?

795
00:32:15,180 --> 00:32:15,500
I...

796
00:32:17,511 --> 00:32:18,740
I don't want to say anything.

797
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:21,260
I have no idea.

798
00:32:24,155 --> 00:32:26,355
I have never had any idea
since I was a child.

799
00:32:34,060 --> 00:32:35,140
You have ideas.

800
00:32:37,420 --> 00:32:38,500
You're just too sensible

801
00:32:41,300 --> 00:32:41,940
and obedient.

802
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:45,380
Sometimes,

803
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:48,380
you're so sensible

804
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,220
that you distress me a little.

805
00:32:56,300 --> 00:32:56,660
Alright.

806
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:58,400
Go to bed early.

807
00:33:02,933 --> 00:33:04,220
I'll turn off the light for you.

808
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:05,260
Okay.

809
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:08,220
Mom.

810
00:33:15,333 --> 00:33:16,111
Good night.

811
00:33:20,860 --> 00:33:21,666
Good night.

812
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:04,140
Have you ever played

813
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:05,860
with Lian Jin?

814
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:07,900
No.

815
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:09,540
I only met him once.

816
00:34:09,622 --> 00:34:11,044
Every time I go to Grandpa's place,

817
00:34:11,044 --> 00:34:12,740
he stays in the study
and doesn't come out.

818
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:14,580
That kid is a little weird.

819
00:34:15,066 --> 00:34:15,740
Right? Shen Qing.

820
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:20,700
Mom, I'm done.

821
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:21,340
Enjoy your meal.

822
00:34:22,540 --> 00:34:24,300
I'm talking to you,
but you're ignoring me?

823
00:34:24,577 --> 00:34:25,620
I need to make a report.

824
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:27,380
You have to work?

825
00:34:27,540 --> 00:34:28,660
Close the door.

826
00:34:28,860 --> 00:34:29,940
Don't let us bother you.

827
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:30,860
Okay.

828
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:34,300
Don't just sit there
after you finish eating.

829
00:34:34,300 --> 00:34:35,300
Walk around.

830
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:36,180
He already sat down.

831
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:41,940
Look, what did I say?

832
00:34:43,300 --> 00:34:44,980
Don't make trouble.
Let your father work.

833
00:34:57,740 --> 00:34:59,420
Did they mention marriage?

834
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:00,140
No.

835
00:35:00,500 --> 00:35:01,340
I guess...

836
00:35:02,300 --> 00:35:02,700
Duole.

837
00:35:02,911 --> 00:35:03,940
Why are you lying there?

838
00:35:04,780 --> 00:35:05,580
It's genetics.

839
00:35:08,060 --> 00:35:08,860
Ignore him for now.

840
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:10,820
I guess

841
00:35:11,260 --> 00:35:13,020
the old man is still under observation.

842
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:14,260
If I were Ms. Lian,

843
00:35:14,260 --> 00:35:15,500
I'd like to observe too.

844
00:35:15,820 --> 00:35:16,180
Right?

845
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,740
Can this stepfather
tolerate his stepson?

846
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:23,340
Ms. Lian is amazing.

847
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:26,740
Okay, just perform well.

848
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,577
I'll play a game with Lian Jin

849
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,911
and give Grandpa extra points.

850
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:32,540
Shut up.

851
00:35:33,088 --> 00:35:34,911
Go. Go back to your room and play.

852
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:36,700
Hurry up.

853
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:37,420
Hurry.

854
00:35:37,540 --> 00:35:38,060
Go.

855
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:46,860
Mom.

856
00:35:48,820 --> 00:35:51,260
Lian Jin
doesn't seem to be in good health.

857
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:57,620
Be careful with this.

858
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:00,340
If they really get married,

859
00:36:00,340 --> 00:36:02,100
he becomes your brother.

860
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:04,260
Maybe he'll change his last name.

861
00:36:06,940 --> 00:36:08,380
If your father-in-law...

862
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:11,500
who will take care of this child?

863
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:13,220
Definitely you and Shen Qing.

864
00:36:14,420 --> 00:36:15,377
When that happens,

865
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:16,100
well...

866
00:36:16,660 --> 00:36:18,300
Work, marriage, and children...

