- Let me take a look.

905
00:37:27,622 --> 00:37:28,200
It's true.

906
00:37:31,860 --> 00:37:34,180
This is oak, solid wood.

907
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:36,060
It's environmentally friendly.

908
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:38,340
You get what you pay for.

909
00:37:40,220 --> 00:37:41,700
You still have to compare prices.

910
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:43,620
It also says solid wood.

911
00:37:45,260 --> 00:37:47,740
Don't believe the advertisement online.

912
00:37:48,420 --> 00:37:49,540
Could I be wrong?

913
00:37:49,540 --> 00:37:51,500
I compared them one by one.

914
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,540
How could I not know?

915
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:55,500
Besides,

916
00:37:56,980 --> 00:37:58,140
I call the shots in my house.

917
00:38:06,700 --> 00:38:07,380
Ding, eat.

918
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:08,660
Shen.

919
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,100
Shen.

920
00:38:10,820 --> 00:38:12,060
You should introduce

921
00:38:12,060 --> 00:38:13,580
your love story.

922
00:38:14,540 --> 00:38:15,140
Yes.

923
00:38:16,380 --> 00:38:16,980
Right?

924
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:20,040
