925
00:38:20,044 --> 00:38:22,260
I had a serious illness a while ago.

926
00:38:22,933 --> 00:38:24,044
Getting hospitalized

927
00:38:24,340 --> 00:38:26,540
is like getting a major repair.
You know?

928
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:30,155
One problem was cured,
but another one appeared.

929
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:32,380
Thanks to our head nurse, Yilian,

930
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,540
for taking good care of me.

931
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:35,740
Without her,

932
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:37,540
I may not be here today.

933
00:38:38,066 --> 00:38:39,500
So how has the hospitalization been

934
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:40,860
during this period?

935
00:38:41,060 --> 00:38:42,020
I cured my disease

936
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:43,700
and gained love.

937
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:46,460
This is a double harvest!

938
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:48,980
- Yes, double harvest.
- Double harvest.

939
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:51,620
If we're not feeling well,

940
00:38:51,980 --> 00:38:54,420
