941
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:56,860
get us an appointment?

942
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:01,500
No problem. You can cut in line.

943
00:39:02,140 --> 00:39:02,940
Okay.

944
00:39:03,577 --> 00:39:05,577
It's all electronic registration now.

945
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:07,920
But feel free to find me anytime
if you're not feeling well.

946
00:39:07,940 --> 00:39:10,260
Okay, I'll create a chat group.

947
00:39:10,420 --> 00:39:11,420
Yes, create a group.

948
00:39:11,420 --> 00:39:13,220
I can send the photos I took today

949
00:39:13,460 --> 00:39:14,380
to the chat group.

950
00:39:14,580 --> 00:39:15,820
- Yes.
- That's right.

951
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:17,420
These old folks

952
00:39:17,844 --> 00:39:19,150
are trying to gain favor with her.

953
00:39:19,260 --> 00:39:20,100
How arrogant.

954
00:39:20,460 --> 00:39:21,100
Yeah.

955
00:39:21,111 --> 00:39:22,860
Modern medicine
is extensive and profound.

956
00:39:23,340 --> 00:39:24,860
Even a doctor won't ask you

957
00:39:25,466 --> 00:39:27,311
to find them if you're not feeling well.

958
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:28,740
It's too much.

959
00:39:28,860 --> 00:39:29,140
Yes.

960
00:39:29,140 --> 00:39:29,955
Come, let's drink.

961
00:39:29,980 --> 00:39:31,860
Don't forget to take a photo for us.

962
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:33,340
Take a photo for us.

963
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:34,980
Look at Shen.

964
00:39:35,340 --> 00:39:36,980
He was all dramatic

965
00:39:38,220 --> 00:39:40,180
during the Mid-Autumn Poetry Festival.

966
00:39:40,300 --> 00:39:40,900
Yeah.

967
00:39:41,644 --> 00:39:43,980
He even needed his grandson
to support him as he walked.

968
00:39:46,220 --> 00:39:49,740
I thought he couldn't recover.

969
00:39:52,220 --> 00:39:53,180
Men

970
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:56,300
must love even after death.

971
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,740
Love keeps them alive.

972
00:39:59,220 --> 00:39:59,980
Let's eat.

973
00:40:00,300 --> 00:40:01,180
Let's dig in.

974
00:40:13,900 --> 00:40:14,940
Look.

975
00:40:16,780 --> 00:40:19,900
Your dad, who is nearly 70 years old,
is enjoying life.

976
00:40:20,220 --> 00:40:21,100
What are you doing?

977
00:40:22,220 --> 00:40:22,980
What am I doing?

978
00:40:23,288 --> 00:40:25,700
I'm earning money to support my family.
What am I doing?

979
00:40:31,420 --> 00:40:33,420
If one day I die first,

980
00:40:34,380 --> 00:40:35,900
you'll definitely be like your dad.

981
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,420
You'll dye your hair,

982
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,300
date,

983
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:41,020
and bring home
someone 20 years younger than you.

984
00:40:43,540 --> 00:40:44,340
Ms. Liu Lina.

985
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:46,380
I've had enough of you lately.

986
00:40:46,940 --> 00:40:48,260
I'm telling you very seriously

987
00:40:48,580 --> 00:40:50,260
that my mom's position in my dad's heart

988
00:40:50,260 --> 00:40:51,620
is irreplaceable.

989
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:52,420
How do you know?

990
00:40:52,420 --> 00:40:53,340
Don't ask me how I know.

991
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:54,140
I just know.

992
00:40:57,580 --> 00:40:58,140
Lina.

993
00:40:59,288 --> 00:41:01,100
We've known each other
since freshman year.

994
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:02,780
We've experienced many things together.

995
00:41:03,300 --> 00:41:03,820
Without you,

996
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:06,460
I wouldn't even quit the Big Four
to start my own business.

997
00:41:07,900 --> 00:41:10,690
I wouldn't be able to hold it together
over the years while Mom was sick.

998
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:12,340
A married couple is not only partners.

999
00:41:12,444 --> 00:41:13,444
But more importantly,

1000
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:15,300
we're comrades-in-arms.

1001
00:41:15,660 --> 00:41:17,220
The bond where we fight side by side

1002
00:41:17,220 --> 00:41:19,460
and support each other
through thick and thin,

1003
00:41:19,900 --> 00:41:20,740
