1004
00:41:24,100 --> 00:41:25,460
I still envy Ms. Lian.

1005
00:41:26,500 --> 00:41:28,060
Look how good your dad is to her.

1006
00:41:28,380 --> 00:41:29,940
That's what love looks like.

1007
00:41:31,540 --> 00:41:32,740
Every relationship

1008
00:41:32,740 --> 00:41:35,460
